title: [Nielira Harbor, Gardens]
description: Sun-lightened pergolas of ashen haon branches are scattered across the sweeping gardens, shading the bronze-wrought chairs encircling honeycomb-patterned tables nestled on the lawn.  An arched ebony-planked bridge curves over the pale blue waters of the small pond, the embankment spotted in patches of verdant cattails and soft tufts of grass.  Geometric beds framed in limestone are abloom with vibrant flora, the budding verdure graced by tiny honeybees buzzing between the well-tended plots.
paths: Obvious paths: north, northeast, southeast, south, west
